headline: Asana to Announce Second Quarter Fiscal Year 2026 Financial Results on Wednesday, September 3, 2025
summary: SAN FRANCISCO, August 01, 2025--Asana, Inc. (NYSE: ASAN)(LTSE: ASAN), a leading work management platform for human + AI coordination, announced today that it will release financial results for the second quarter fiscal year 2026 on Wednesday, September 3, after the close of the U.S. markets.
